<text>is a Japanese voice actress and narrator. She was previously affiliated with Vi-Vo and is currently affiliated with Aoni Production. Her major roles include, Nico Robin in &quot;One Piece&quot;, Ritsuko Akagi in &quot;Neon Genesis Evangelion&quot;, Sonia in &quot;Eureka Seven&quot; and Nurse Joy in &quot;Pokémon&quot;.

