<doc id="771535" wikidata="Q5983" url="?curid=771535" title="Evijärvi">
<text>Evijärvi is a municipality of Finland. It is located in the Southern Ostrobothnia region. The municipality has a population of () and covers an area of of which is water. The population density is .

Neighbouring municipalities are Kauhava, Kronoby, Lappajärvi, Pedersöre and Veteli.

The municipality is unilingually Finnish.

==Notable people born in Evijärvi==
*Jalmari Linna (1891–1954)
*Aleksi Kiviaho (1913–1986)
*Ilmari Linna (1917–1981)
*Tea Ista (1932–2014)
*Esko Ahonen (1955–)

